@startuml Onboarding Flow
!theme vibrant
title LilyFit - User Onboarding Flow

actor User
participant "OnboardingScreen" as Onboard
participant "PageController" as PageCtrl
participant "UserProfile" as Profile
participant "SupabaseService" as Supabase
participant "AppProvider" as Provider
participant "HomeScreen" as Home

User -> Onboard: Start Onboarding
activate Onboard

Onboard -> PageCtrl: Initialize with 6 pages
activate PageCtrl

== Step 1: Name ==
Onboard --> User: "What's your name?"
User -> Onboard: Enter name
User -> Onboard: Click "Next"
Onboard -> Profile: Set name
PageCtrl -> PageCtrl: animateToPage(1)

== Step 2: Gender ==
Onboard --> User: "Select your gender"
User -> Onboard: Choose (Male/Female/Other)
User -> Onboard: Click "Next"
Onboard -> Profile: Set gender
PageCtrl -> PageCtrl: animateToPage(2)

== Step 3: Age ==
Onboard --> User: "How old are you?"
User -> Onboard: Adjust age slider (10-100)
User -> Onboard: Click "Next"
Onboard -> Profile: Set age
PageCtrl -> PageCtrl: animateToPage(3)

== Step 4: Physical Stats ==
Onboard --> User: "Your measurements"
User -> Onboard: Toggle unit system\n(kg/cm or lbs/ft)
User -> Onboard: Adjust weight slider
User -> Onboard: Adjust height slider
User -> Onboard: Click "Next"
Onboard -> Profile: Set weight, height, units
PageCtrl -> PageCtrl: animateToPage(4)

== Step 5: Activity Level ==
Onboard --> User: "How active are you?"
User -> Onboard: Select activity level:\n- Sedentary (1.2x)\n- Light (1.375x)\n- Moderate (1.55x)\n- Active (1.725x)\n- Very Active (1.9x)
User -> Onboard: Click "Next"
Onboard -> Profile: Set activityLevel
PageCtrl -> PageCtrl: animateToPage(5)

== Step 6: Goal Selection ==
Onboard --> User: "What's your goal?"
User -> Onboard: Select goal:\n- Fat Loss (-500 cal)\n- Maintenance (0 cal)\n- Muscle Gain (+300 cal)
User -> Onboard: Click "Complete"

Onboard -> Profile: Set goal
Onboard -> Profile: calculateTargets()
activate Profile

Profile -> Profile: Calculate BMR using\nMifflin-St Jeor Equation
Profile -> Profile: Apply activity multiplier
Profile -> Profile: Apply goal adjustment
Profile -> Profile: Calculate macro splits:\n- Protein (4 cal/g)\n- Carbs (4 cal/g)\n- Fat (9 cal/g)
Profile --> Onboard: Targets calculated
deactivate Profile

Onboard --> User: Show loading

Onboard -> Supabase: saveUserProfile(profile)
activate Supabase

alt Save Failed
    Supabase --> Onboard: Error
    deactivate Supabase
    Onboard --> User: Show error dialog

else Save Successful
    Supabase --> Onboard: Profile saved
    deactivate Supabase

    Onboard -> Provider: completeOnboarding(profile)
    activate Provider

    Provider -> Provider: Save to SharedPreferences
    Provider -> Provider: Mark as onboarded
    Provider -> Provider: Add initial weight entry
    Provider --> Onboard: Onboarding complete
    deactivate Provider

    Onboard -> Home: Navigate (pushReplacement)
    activate Home
    Home --> User: Welcome! Show dashboard
    deactivate Home
end

deactivate PageCtrl
deactivate Onboard

note right of Profile
  **Calculations Example:**
  - Gender: Male, Age: 25
  - Weight: 75kg, Height: 175cm
  - Activity: Moderate (1.55x)
  - Goal: Muscle Gain

  BMR = 10*75 + 6.25*175 - 5*25 + 5
      = 750 + 1093.75 - 125 + 5
      = 1723.75 kcal

  TDEE = 1723.75 * 1.55 = 2671.8 kcal
  Target = 2671.8 + 300 = 2972 kcal

  Macros:
  - Protein: 30% = 223g
  - Carbs: 45% = 334g
  - Fat: 25% = 83g
end note

@enduml

